<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Website Samid</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        
        body { font-family: sans-serif; }
        
        .header {
            background: #c0392b;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }
        
        .menu-btn {
            font-size: 24px;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            margin-right: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .sidebar {
            background: #c0392b;
            color: white;
            width: 250px;
            height: 100vh;
            position: fixed;
            left: -250px;
            top: 0;
            padding-top: 60px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            z-index: 99;
        }
        
        .sidebar.active {
            left: 0;
        }
        
        .sidebar a {
            display: block;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #a93226;
        }
        
        .sidebar a:hover {
            background: #a93226;
        }
        
        .content {
            margin-top: 60px;
            padding: 20px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        
        .overlay {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            z-index: 98;
        }
        
        .overlay.active {
            display: block;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <button class="menu-btn" onclick="toggleSidebar()">☰</button>
        <h3>SAMID KEREN</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="overlay" id="overlay" onclick="toggleSidebar()"></div>

    <div class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">About</a>
        <a href="#">Services</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h1>Selamat Datang di Website Gue</h1>
        <p>Sekarang sidebarnya bisa buka-tutup. Klik tombol ☰ di pojok kiri atas bro!</p>
        <p>Kalo klik area gelap, sidebarnya ketutup otomatis.</p>
    </div>

    <script>
        function toggleSidebar() {
            document.getElementById('sidebar').classList.toggle('active');
            document.getElementById('overlay
